* Translation:

Once upon a time,
There was a small nougat walking around
(Lilalilali lalalalala)
He was happy

But he had no more house,
Was walking without a purpose
(Lilalilali lalalalala
Prün bambam poum)

Huuuh, an evil coyote
Pay attention, little nougat
But the nougat defends itself
